Who Is Eligible for an Urgent Personal Loan?

  • Indian citizen aged 21 years and above
  • A salaried individual
  • Minimum monthly income ₹35,000
  • Aadhaar & PAN Card
  • Last 3 months salary' slip
  • Last 6 months' bank statement
  • Address proof (Utility bill, rental agreement, etc.)

Personal Loan Criteria – Know Before You Apply

We follow transparent and responsible lending practices. Here are our loan details:

  • Loan Amount:₹10,000 to ₹2,00,000
  • ROI:Up to 30%
  • APR:Up to 35%
  • Age Requirement:21 to 55 years
  • Processing Fee:Up to 5%
  • Loan Tenure:3 months to 12 months

Instant Personal Loan Example – EMI & Interest Overview

For a loan of ₹20,000 over 90 days at an interest rate of 30%:

Loan Amount:
₹20,000
Tenure:
3 months
Total Interest:
₹1,500
Processing Fees (PF) + GST:
₹1,000 + ₹180 = ₹1,180
Disbursed Amount:
₹18,820
Total Repayable Amount:
₹21,500
Monthly EMI Repayable:
₹7,167

Note: The above calculations are for illustration purposes only. Your actual EMI and repayment terms may vary. Processing fees and GST are deducted upfront during loan disbursal.
